<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_306_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l13"><expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd ob das peter <expan>volkm<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein möcht / auf nu freıtag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l14">ʒu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag gen Vlme ʒuleıhen etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l15"><expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Daʒ Peter . <expan>volkm<ex>er</ex></expan> als nechten spat erſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l16">herheim <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt von dem tag ʒu Poparten . So ſol auf nu ſunn = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l17">tag ein tag bey vns <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . von des vnfrıds <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der ʒwıſchen . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l18"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vmb vns ıſt / daʒ wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> rats </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l19">ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns bedürffen vnd ſo gehlıng nıht wol auf = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l20">bringen <expan>mochte<ex>n</ex></expan> der eẅch bey dem tag nucʒlıch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l21">eẅr <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> das von vns in gut ʒu verſteen Denn wo wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l24"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l25"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Jacobȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_306" id="152r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
